item.title: 6 Projects in 6 Months Challenge
item.description: I spent the last 10+yrs to code, and the last 4yrs in the startup ecosystem. During all that time I was focus on the product more than anything else. I need a change. I want to learn the other parts of building a product and I want something challenging! So I decided to (try to) launch 6 products in the next 6 months! I want to remove my developer bias As a coder, you always want to build stuff.
